    <published>2017-01-16T11:33:47.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-09-07T14:36:59.629Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>树莓派的常用功能配置：</p><ul><li>Vnc viewer</li><li>Vsftpd</li></ul><a id="more"></a><h3 id="1-Vnc-viewer"><a href="#1-Vnc-viewer" class="headerlink" title="1. Vnc viewer"></a>1. Vnc viewer</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo apt-get install tightvncviewer</span><br><span class="line">$ tightvncserver</span><br><span class="line">$ vncserver :1 -geometry 800x600 -depth 24</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-Vsftpd"><a href="#2-Vsftpd" class="headerlink" title="2. Vsftpd"></a>2. Vsftpd</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo apt-get install vsftpd</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo service vsftpd start</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;树莓派的常用功能配置：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Vnc viewer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Vsftpd&lt;/li&gt;
